### Phase 3: Redis Session Verification

---

#### [NEW] [redis_health.go](file:///c:/projects/ReMS/backend/services/core/redis_health.go)

`RedisHealthService` with:
- `Ping(ctx)` — `redis.Ping()` 
- `GetStats(ctx)` — returns key count, memory, uptime
- `VerifySessionIntegrity(ctx, userID)` — checks session keys match the user's session set, cleans orphans

---

#### [NEW] [redis.go](file:///c:/projects/ReMS/backend/config/redis.go)

`NewRedisClient(host, port, password string, db int) *redis.Client` — centralized Redis client factory.

