### Phase 4: Svelte Frontend

---

#### [NEW] `frontend/` directory (SvelteKit project)

Initialize with `npx -y sv create ./` in non-interactive mode.

Key pages and components:

| Path | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `src/routes/login/+page.svelte` | Login form with 2FA support |
| `src/routes/register/+page.svelte` | Registration form |
| `src/routes/(app)/+layout.svelte` | Authenticated layout with sidebar/navbar |
| `src/routes/(app)/dashboard/+page.svelte` | Main dashboard with KPI cards |
| `src/routes/(app)/restaurants/+page.svelte` | Restaurant list + CRUD |
| `src/routes/(app)/orders/+page.svelte` | Order management |
| `src/routes/(app)/menu/+page.svelte` | Menu management |
| `src/routes/(app)/inventory/+page.svelte` | Inventory management |
| `src/routes/(app)/analytics/+page.svelte` | Analytics dashboard |
| `src/routes/(app)/settings/+page.svelte` | User settings |
| `src/lib/api/client.ts` | Fetch wrapper with auth interceptor + token refresh |
| `src/lib/stores/auth.ts` | Svelte store for auth state |
| `src/lib/components/` | Reusable UI components (DataTable, Modal, Chart, etc.) |

**Design**: Dark theme with glassmorphism, Inter font, vibrant accent colors, smooth transitions.

